Fast-rising Nigerian artist Joeboy has released the music video to his latest single, “Beginning”. Described as a song that “captures that space between the friend zone and romance with its succinct refrain: “I’m beginning to begin to fall in love.” Joeboy confesses his feelings for his love interest in the Killertunes produced song. “Beginning” is the follow-up song to his previous smash hit single “Baby” which earned massive airplay and topped music playlists across the country. Joeboy is a product of Mr. Eazi‘s emPawa Africa, an incubator programme committed to funding and providing career guidance for young artists. Watch “Beginning” below: 